stiff lamb disease
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a disease of the muscles of lambs and calves causing difficulty in walking and possibly eventual death.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
